result.title: Hack me! (Codeforces Round #282 (Div. 2))
result.content:
Quite delayed, but here we have stats about hacks in Codeforces Round #282 (Div. 2).

Previous posts can be found here, including div1.

Stats

495D - Одержимость строкой 0 0 0 0 3 (27.27%) 8 (72.73%) 11
495E - Помощь нуждающимся 0 0 0 0 0 0 0

Hacks and possible hacks description

495A - Цифровой индикатор

That was an interesting problem, but the hacks were pretty simple — the pretests weren't checking every digits, so when someone made a mistake, we can make use of it.

Congratulation to all hackers, because only 47 solutions (2.65%) didn't pass final tests. :)

495B - Модулярные уравнения

The most popular hack was pretty simple:

1000000000 1

Solutions with complexity O(|b - a|) resulted with TLE.

495C - Сокровище

The hacks were simple strings with no solutions like:

(#(

(((#)((

(#(()

It was also test #14 (look below):

((#)(

Pretty and deadly :)
